description: Legislatures Support Project (2011-2015). Includes Inception plan and support to National Assembly and Zanzibar House of Representatives.

subproject.description: Orientation Programme for the new National Assembly  of Tanzania and the Zanzibar House of Representatives in the context of the Government of the National Unity held; Standing Orders of the Zanzibar House of Representatives revised and passed by the House in-line with the requirements of the Government of National Unity; Legislature Support Project (LSP) document drafted and approved; and the LSP operational.

subproject.corporate outcome: Electoral laws, processes and institutions strengthen inclusive participation and professional electoral administration. strengthen parliamentary function and build democratic culture through civic education.
